Package src

Class TranspositionTable

  • java.lang.Object
    • src.TranspositionTable
  • public class TranspositionTable
extends java.lang.Object
    This method contains all the information of the transposition table of the zobrist hashing method. Also, it provides the needed methods to set, update or get this information.
